flowchart TD
  A[Build queued] --> B[Worker leases job]
  B --> C[Runner executes build in container]
  C -->|success| D[Store artifacts + update status]
  D --> E[Emit built event + logs]
  C -->|failure| F[Auto-fix evaluates logs]
  F -->|apply recipes| G[Retry with backoff]
  G --> B
  F -->|no recipes or blocked| H[Mark failed]
  H --> E
  D --> I{Repair enabled?}
  I -->|yes| J[Run repair tool + store repaired wheel]
  I -->|no| K[Done]
  J --> K
